tions.yaml` (add send message steps)\n2. `.maestro/scripts/run-e2e.sh` (fix `_` 
inclusion and backend deps)\n\nThat\'s 2 files. But `_enter_chat_actions.yaml` i
s used by `enter_chat.yaml`. If we add send steps there, `enter_chat.yaml` will 
also send a message. That might be okay, but it\'s mixing concerns. Better to cr
eate a new `_send_message_actions.yaml` and `send_message.yaml`.\n\nBut creating
two new files plus modifying `run-e2e.sh` is 3 files. Exactly at the limit.\n\nH
owever, we also need to update the seed script if we want a system message. That
would be 4 files.\n\nAlternatively, we can just fix `run-e2e.sh` (1 file) and cr
eate `send_message.yaml` + `_send_message_actions.yaml` (2 new files). Total 3.\
